No. 173,

Misc.

St. Elmo et al. v. Campbell, U. S. District Judge. George W. Crank and Harry G. Fins for petitioners. John C. Melaniphy and Sydney R. Drebin for the Neighborhood Redevelopment Commission of the City of Chicago, and William H. Dillon for the South West Hyde Park Neighborhood Redevelopment Corporation.
